By adding or using NAVRE in your server, you agree to comply with these Terms, as well as Discord’s own Terms of Service and Community Guidelines. If you do not agree with any part of these Terms, please do not use the Bot.

These Terms are designed to ensure that the Bot remains safe, useful, and respectful for all users. 

Please read them carefully.

