1. Description of Service
NAVRE is a Discord bot designed to improve server functionality by providing features such as:

• Automated welcome and leave messages.

• Role assignment and management.

• Server rules display.

• Movie night polls and reminders.

• Other utility or entertainment features.

These features may be modified, expanded, or discontinued at any time without notice.


